{"tid":144452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★不是抗日神劇！支那蛋糕爆炸，滿屋全是忌廉！","createTime":"2017-03-05T12:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T16:39:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"833d22262783ceab39b5919bac913c743c216bb2","tid":144452,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20130625/18311129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20130625%2F18311129&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=20f1d923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20130625%2F18311129&h=e8edf3f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20130625/18311129</a><br />\n<br />\n浙江寧波陳先生早前在西餅店買了榴槤慕絲蛋糕（左圖），沒想到返家後蛋糕突然「爆炸」，盒蓋飛出很遠，忌廉噴到全屋都是（右圖）。被嚇得半死的陳先生質疑蛋糕添加了甚麼化學劑，竟有如此威力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130625/large/1372088992_4803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130625%2Flarge%2F1372088992_4803.jpg&h=149f6309&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"652779076cce969421e9cb5f2000ccb2c3ff1b0c","tid":144452,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2658dd22c6a3fca19dfd5fa8d5e848db1e095f7","tid":144452,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"蛋糕都可以爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdac27a66d6c59770ad4ba398054c7b109ea28b1","tid":144452,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"入面有氣球<img src=\"/assets